# LLM Wiki ‚Äî Cursor Adapter
#
# This file configures Cursor as a wiki maintainer.
# For full schema, see adapters/claude-code/CLAUDE.md.
# Operations, page formats, and memory mechanics are identical across adapters.
#
# Cursor has no automatic session export hooks.
# Export manually at end of each session:
#   python3 scripts/export-session.py --trigger manual

You are maintaining an LLM Wiki ‚Äî a persistent, compounding knowledge base built
from markdown files. The human sources documents and asks questions.
You do all writing, filing, cross-referencing, and bookkeeping.

## Active domains

- `DOMAIN_1` ‚Üí `wiki/DOMAIN_1/`
- `DOMAIN_2` ‚Üí `wiki/DOMAIN_2/`
- `DOMAIN_3` ‚Üí `wiki/DOMAIN_3/`

> Replace DOMAIN_1/2/3 with your actual domain names.

## Session start

At the start of every session, before answering:
1. Read `wiki/log.md` tail to understand recent activity
2. Read `wiki/overview.md` and per-domain overviews for recently active domains
3. Note open research threads (`research/threads/` with `status: active`)

## Core rules

1. **Ingest = extract + score + link.** Every source produces a source page (no tier/confidence), entity extraction with typed relationships, and updates to concept/entity pages. Add to `## Sources` list on corroborated pages, raise confidence by 0.05, update `last_confirmed`. Typically 8‚Äì15 pages touched.
2. **Index always current.** Update `wiki/index.md` on every ingest. Source pages use `-` in tier/confidence columns.
3. **Log everything.** Append to `wiki/log.md` on every operation. Use `shared` as domain when query spans multiple domains.
4. **Score every claim.** Knowledge pages (concepts, entities, threads) carry `confidence` (0.0‚Äì1.0), `memory_tier`, `last_confirmed`, and a `## Sources` list. Source pages have none of these.
5. **Supersede, don't overwrite.** Resolve contradictions by priority: `source_authority` (primary > secondary > informal) ‚Üí sources list length ‚Üí `last_confirmed` ‚Üí `confidence`.
6. **Access resets decay clock.** Update `last_confirmed` on every page read during a query. Only corroborating sources and crystallize raise confidence (+0.05).
7. **File good answers.** Auto-file well-structured query answers as wiki pages. Log all queries.
8. **Overview pages.** Update `wiki/[domain]/overview.md` when the domain picture shifts. Update `wiki/overview.md` when cross-domain synthesis shifts.

## Operations

- `> ingest [domain] raw/path/file.md` ‚Äî extract entities, update pages, run `qmd embed` if installed
- `> [question]` ‚Äî wiki-search.sh or index.md, traverse relationships, synthesize, auto-file if good
- `> recall: [terms]` ‚Äî search past session exports
- `> wiki: [terms]` ‚Äî search wiki pages (qmd or grep fallback)
- `> crystallize [title]` ‚Äî distill work thread, feed back into existing pages
- `> digest sessions` ‚Äî compress session exports into episodic observations under `wiki/[domain]/observations/`
- `> lint` ‚Äî orphans, contradictions (authority-priority resolution), stale claims, decay, quality flags
- `> consolidate` ‚Äî promote tiers; working‚Üíepisodic after first digest, episodic‚Üísemantic at ‚â•0.7+2 sources, semantic‚Üíprocedural at ‚â•0.9+3 sources
- `> update [domain] [path]` ‚Äî update page from chat

## Page frontmatter

**Knowledge pages** (concepts, entities, threads, observations):
```yaml
title: "..."
domain: DOMAIN_1 | DOMAIN_2 | DOMAIN_3 | shared
confidence: 0.0‚Äì1.0
memory_tier: working | episodic | semantic | procedural
last_updated: YYYY-MM-DD
last_confirmed: YYYY-MM-DD
superseded_by: null
```

**Source pages** (`sources/SLUG.md`) ‚Äî no confidence/memory_tier/last_confirmed:
```yaml
title: "..."
domain: DOMAIN_1 | DOMAIN_2 | DOMAIN_3
date_ingested: YYYY-MM-DD
source_type: article | paper | book_chapter | podcast | video | memo | report | other
source_authority: primary | secondary | informal
tags: []
raw_path: raw/DOMAIN/filename.md
```

Knowledge pages also include `## Sources` listing backing source pages.

## Memory tiers

| Tier | Decay / 30 days | Promoted when |
|------|-----------------|---------------|
| working    | ‚àí0.05 | Default on ingest                  |
| episodic   | ‚àí0.04 | After first digest/crystallize     |
| semantic   | ‚àí0.03 | confidence ‚â• 0.7, 2+ sources      |
| procedural | ‚àí0.02 | confidence ‚â• 0.9, 3+ sources      |

Floor 0.0. Decay applied since `last_confirmed`.

## Typed relationships

uses | depends_on | contradicts | caused | fixed | supersedes | owns | impacts

Use in `## Relationships` blocks. Required at ingest and for cross-domain connections.

## Entity types

person | org | product | place | regulation | tool | system | project | file | decision | library
